Show configuration help for 'usb PS4' controller:confctrl_ph.sh -p help -c usb -t PS4 | more
Show configuration help for 'Sony Wireless Adapter PS4' controller:confctrl_ph.sh -p help -c sonywadapt -t PS4 | more
Show configuration help for 'bluetooth PS4' controller:confctrl_ph.sh -p help -c bluetooth -t PS4 | more
Configure 'bluetooth PS4' controller(s):confctrl_ph.sh -p prompt -t PS4
Go to 'Main' menu:ph_show_menu Main
Go to 'Controllers' menu:ph_show_menu Controllers
Open Shell to home directory (Type 'CTRL-D' to return):cd;/bin/bash
Return to previous screen:return
